{"id":26790,"date":"2018-09-06T12:40:55","date_gmt":"2018-09-06T08:40:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=26790"},"modified":"2023-06-06T18:36:20","modified_gmt":"2023-06-06T14:36:20","slug":"weighty-sakinah-divine-wahy","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/09\/06\/weighty-sakinah-divine-wahy\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Revelation: Weighty calm of the Prophet\u2019s divine inspiration"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Zayd ibn Thabit reported: I was sitting to the side of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, one day as the revelation came to him. The Prophet was overcome with calm, and his thigh fell upon my thigh as the calm overtook him. By Allah, I have never found anything heavier than the thigh of the Messenger of Allah, and then he was released from it. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Write, O Zayd<\/strong>.\u201d I took a shoulder bone and the Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Write: Not equal are those who stay back and those who wage jihad among the believers<\/strong>,\u201d until the end of the verse, \u201c<strong>\u2026 a great reward<\/strong>,\u201d (4:95). So I wrote that on a shoulder bone.<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 21664<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u062b\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u062a\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u0650\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0639\u0650\u062f\u064c \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u062c\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0625\u0650\